it.uniud.mads.jlibbig.core

Class AbstractNamed

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.uniud.mads.jlibbig.core.AbstractNamed
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Named
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Control

    public abstract class AbstractNamed
extends java.lang.Object
implements Named
    Describes a name identified entity and provides some name generation methods. Name generation is thread safe but it is not guaranteed to be universally unique (in time and space). The same name can be generated by different machines and runs.
